data.description: Maintenance free living w/NO restrictions! Built in 2016, this property features 4 bedrooms/ 2.5 bathrooms, level yard w/ fenced in back, new large out building w/electricity, and separate canopy for grilling or outdoor seating - all included. Note: This property has a designated parking space for a LARGE RV.  Inside features a spacious kitchen w/island, upgraded cabinets and granite tops opens to a separate dining area and living area.  Oversized primary suite and bath includes large walk-in closet. Unique trey ceilings with embedded lighting.  Remaining bedrooms are spacious with ample closet space as well. *INCLUDED are 2 handicap stair lifts: 1 from main to second level. 2nd from garage to main level* (These could easily be removed if not needed) **Also included are 4 mounted flatscreen TVs**This home is centrally located to interstates, shopping, downtown, restaurants, hospitals and much more.** Refrigerator and portable gray electric fireplace do not convey **
